1. Ja *zaustavim* automobil kad vidim crveno svetlo. (I stop the car when I see the red light.)
2. *Zaustavila* sam se na trenutak da se pozdravim sa prijateljicom. (I stopped for a moment to say goodbye to my friend.)
3. Ako ne *zaustavite* navalu emocija, možete izgubiti kontrolu. (If you don't stop the surge of emotions, you can lose control.)
4. Želim da *zaustavim* ovu nepravdu i da pronađem rešenje za sve nas. (I want to stop this injustice and find a solution for all of us.)
5. Kad *zaustaviš* film, nemoj zaboraviti da ga nastaviš gledati kasnije. (When you stop the movie, don't forget to continue watching it later.)
6. *Zaustavi* se i razmisli o svom postupku pre nego što doneseš odluku. (Stop and think about your actions before making a decision.)
7. Oni su *zaustavili* putnički voz zbog sumnjivog paketa. (They stopped the passenger train because of a suspicious package.)
8. Ukoliko *zaustavimo* globalno zagrevanje, spasimo prirodu i životinje. (If we stop global warming, we can save nature and animals.)
9. Molim vas da me *zaustavite* ako grešim. (Please stop me if I'm wrong.)
10. Kada *zaustavite* proces, nećete moći nastaviti sa radom dok ne pokrenete ponovo. (When you stop the process, you won't be able to continue working until you restart it.)